'''線索細胞'''（Clue cells）是描述表面上沾滿[[细菌|细菌]]的[[阴道|阴道]][[上皮組織|上皮細胞]]，為[[细菌性阴道病|細菌性陰道病]]的[[醫學徵象|醫學徵象]]，特別是[[加德纳氏菌属|陰道加德纳氏菌]]（''Gardnerella vaginalis''）所引起的症狀<ref name="pmid3493202">{{cite journal|title=In vitro adhesiveness and biotype of Gardnerella vaginalis strains in relation to the occurrence of clue cells in vaginal discharges|date=February 1987|journal=Genitourinary medicine|issue=1|doi=10.1136/sti.63.1.47|volume=63|pages=47–53|pmc=1194007|pmid=3493202|vauthors=Scott TG, Smyth CJ, Keane CT}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{cite journal|title=Haemophilus vaginalis vaginitis: A newly defined specific infection previously classified "nonspecific" vaginitis|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_american-journal-of-obstetrics-and-gynecology_1955-05_69_5/page/962|last=Gardner|first=Herman|date=May 1955|journal=American Journal of Obstetrics and Gynecology|issue=5|doi=10.1016/0002-9378(55)90095-8|volume=69|pages=962–976|pmid=14361525|author2=Dukes, Charles}}<!--|accessdate=24 January 2013--></ref>。此徵象最初由 Gardner 和 Dukes 等人命名<ref name=":0" />。

感染細菌性陰道炎的患者，陰道容易出現魚腥味的灰白色[[阴道分泌物|分泌物]]，陰道[[pH值|pH值]]也會從酸性的4.5上升到5.5。

